---
import Page from "../../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page class="m-0 p-0 bg-darkest text-almost font-switzer leading-normal">
  <div class="mx-4 md:mx-auto md:max-w-[700px]">
    <div class="pt-12 pb-6 md:pt-24 md:pb-12 max-w-[500px]">
      <h1 class="font-plein font-bold text-8xl md:text-9xl text-sun">
        Trump<br />D.O.G.E.
      </h1>
      <h2 class="py-8 text-2xl md:text-4xl text-medium">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div
      class="pt-10 pb-24 md:pt-20 md:pb-48 text-xl md:text-2xl text-almost/80 font-switzer space-y-8 border-t border-t-dark"
    >
      <p class="font-plein font-bold text-sun text-2xl md:text-3xl">
        What is Trump D.O.G.E.?
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="text-white font-semibold"
          ><a
            href="https://www.trumpdoge.org/"
            target="_blank"
            class="underline hover:text-sun transition-colors duration-200"
            >Trump D.O.G.E.</a
          ></span
        > is an online gathering place for the <span class="text-light-medium"
          >tech community</span
        > to help the incoming Trump administration identify its top priorities
          for government efficiency.
      </p>
      <p class="font-plein font-bold text-sun text-2xl md:text-3xl">
        Who is behind this?
      </p>
      <p>
        Trump D.O.G.E. is a project of <span class="text-white font-semibold"
          ><a
            href="/"
            target="_blank"
            class="underline hover:text-sun transition-colors duration-200"
            >Front Seat</a
          ></span
        >, a small team of tech entrepreneurs based in Seattle.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Page>
